<HEADLINE> Villeneuve Withdraws Appeal </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, October 16 (Xinhua) -- The Williams team withdrew their
appeal Thursday against the disqualification of Jacques Villeneuve
from last weekend's Japanese Grand Prix, reports said.
</P>
<P>
Consequently, Germany's Michael Schumacher of Ferrari leads
Canada's Villeneuve in the drivers championship by one point going
into the season-ending Grand Prix at Jerez, Spain on October 26.
</P>
</TEXT>
