<HEADLINE> Wu Yanyan Breaks Women's 200m Individual Medley World Record </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, October 17 (Xinhua) -- Wu Yanyan of China set a new
world record in the women's individual medley by clocking two
minutes and 9.72 seconds at the Eighth National Games here on
Friday.
</P>
<P>
The previous world mark of 2:11.65 was set by Lin Li of China
in the Barcelona Olympic Games in 1992. 
</P>
</TEXT>
