<HEADLINE> Chinese President Meets US Journalists </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, October 17 (Xinhua) -- Chinese President Jiang Zemin
met here today with Robert Kaiser, executive editor of the
Washington Post, and granted an interview to correspondents from
the prestigious US newspaper.
</P>
<P>
Jiang answered questions concerning Sino-US relations, the
international situation, China's economic situation and efforts to
restructure the country's political system.
</P>
