He said peaceful construction is in the best interests of
China, and that it is the common task of the people of all
countries in the world to sum up history, look to the future, and
create a peaceful, stable and prosperous new world.
</P>
<P>
Senior Chinese officials Zeng Qinghong, Liu Huaqiu and Teng
Wensheng were present at the meeting.  
