- - - -
</P>
<P>
ZAGREB -- A patrol of multinational Stabilization Force (SFOR),
consisting of Russian and U.S. soliders, has discovered an
unreported underground arms depot four kilometers south of the
Udrigovo television tower.
</P>
<P>
The SFOR in Tuzla said in a press release Thursday that the
depot contained 250 anti-tank mines, 46 boxes of TNT expolosives
and 21 barrels of enriched petroleum for making napalm bombs. It
is not clear who is the owner of those arms. (Bosnia-SFOR-Arsenal)
</P>
<P>
