Frederick A. Okecho, Uganda's ambassador to China, said his
country and China have enjoyed warm relations and that Uganda
treasures its cooperation with China in political and economic
areas.
</P>
<P>
He also expressed his gratitude to the Chinese government for
its technological aid in support of Uganda's agriculture.
</P>
<P>
