<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Atletico Mineiro Enter Conmebol Cup Semi-finals </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRAZILIA, October 16 (Xinhua) -- Atletico Mineiro of Brazil
drew with America of Cali, Colombia 1-1 in Belo Horizonte, Brazil
on Thursday to enter the semi-finals of the Conmebol Cup soccer
tournament.
</P>
<P>
The first goal of the match was scored by America's defender
Cordona in the 24th minute. Midfielder Edgar of Atletico Mineiro
levelled the score in the 45th minute.
</P>
<P>
After winning the first-leg Match of the quarter-final round
2-1 in Cali, the Brazilian team only needed a tie to win a berth
in the semi-finals. 
</P>
